Title: The Nutcrackers
Plot: Alan defends a mother fighting for custody of her preteen daughters, who happen to be white supremacist singers.Brad and Denise try to persuade a new client against suing God for the death of her husband by lightning, and Denny tries his first major case in a while when he helps a waitress try to regain custody of her anorexic child.
Writer: David E. Kelley, Phoef Sutton, Sanford Golden, Kar
